WEBVTT

00:07.471 --> 00:08.931
I have committed a crime!

00:09.321 --> 00:11.181
Song Mo is innocent!

00:11.481 --> 00:13.811
(Xianqing Gate)
I will testify in person!

00:14.001 --> 00:15.720
Please clear Song Mo's name!

00:15.721 --> 00:16.971
Stop it, Shiying!

00:16.991 --> 00:18.671
- What are you doing?
- Get out of my way!

00:20.791 --> 00:21.870
Have you lost your senses?

00:21.871 --> 00:23.560
Has your son-in-law,

00:23.561 --> 00:24.861
that rascal bewitched you?

00:24.881 --> 00:26.091
Come to your senses!

00:26.361 --> 00:27.821
You deceived your own brother

00:28.151 --> 00:29.700
and framed your niece and nephew-in-law.

00:29.701 --> 00:31.200
You should come to your senses!

00:31.201 --> 00:32.341
You jerk!

00:35.031 --> 00:36.891
I'll slap myself on your behalf.

00:37.121 --> 00:38.371
For so many years,

00:39.311 --> 00:41.461
how many people have been sacrificed,

00:42.311 --> 00:44.011
how many mistakes have been made

00:44.201 --> 00:45.861
just because I'm your younger brother?

00:46.271 --> 00:47.950
I won't make any more mistakes!

00:47.951 --> 00:49.911
You're using Dou Zhao
and Song Mo as sacrifices,

00:50.151 --> 00:52.091
and sacrificing people's lives

00:52.441 --> 00:53.840
for your ambition.

00:53.841 --> 00:55.181
I won't allow it!

00:57.391 --> 00:59.061
An elder brother is like a father.

01:00.271 --> 01:01.891
As long as you bear the Dou name,

01:02.801 --> 01:04.611
you'll do as I say.

01:05.201 --> 01:06.341
Just now

01:08.271 --> 01:10.651
was the last time
I'll ever call you brother.

01:12.201 --> 01:13.621
I will repay you for raising me

01:15.041 --> 01:16.621
with my blood.

01:18.961 --> 01:20.141
What are you doing?

01:20.321 --> 01:21.461
You...

01:21.481 --> 01:23.421
Three strikes of the sword
would sever all ties.

01:23.601 --> 01:25.091
After you strike me three times,

01:25.871 --> 01:27.981
we'll go separate ways.

01:28.151 --> 01:30.061
You and I will no longer be related!

01:32.201 --> 01:33.731
You think I won't do it?

01:34.761 --> 01:35.901
Fine.

01:36.991 --> 01:38.781
I'll grant your wish today.

01:59.071 --> 02:01.141
I've truly misjudged you.

02:03.561 --> 02:05.811
From now on,
you and I are nothing to each other.

02:09.861 --> 02:16.880
(Xianqing Gate)

02:16.881 --> 02:18.230
The two Dou brothers

02:18.231 --> 02:20.131
have fallen to such an extent.

03:52.541 --> 03:56.740
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:56.741 --> 03:59.961
=Episode 32=

04:03.041 --> 04:06.040
Don't think you'll get away
with ruining Lord Qing's plans.

04:06.041 --> 04:08.531
If His Highness finds out
you saved his enemy,

04:08.631 --> 04:09.851
he'll kill you too.

04:12.761 --> 04:15.781
When did His Highness order you
to target the Duchess?

04:16.391 --> 04:18.520
Song Mo hasn't been convicted yet.

04:18.521 --> 04:20.171
And you couldn't wait to make your move.

04:20.751 --> 04:24.021
Do you think His Highness
won't see through your schemes?

04:26.791 --> 04:27.931
Search!

04:45.401 --> 04:47.941
It's just my beloved puppy.

04:48.401 --> 04:51.021
I didn't think the Tengxiang Guards
would care so much.

04:53.211 --> 04:54.351
By the way,

04:55.311 --> 04:57.080
your childhood nickname must have been

04:57.081 --> 04:58.491
Little Dog, right?

04:59.111 --> 05:00.701
No wonder you grew up biting

05:00.751 --> 05:02.581
anyone you see.

05:19.111 --> 05:20.851
His Highness has spoken.

05:21.751 --> 05:23.821
Since you like to play with fire,

05:24.281 --> 05:27.291
it's only fitting I greet you
with flames.

05:27.551 --> 05:31.491
If you admit to forging the contract

05:31.671 --> 05:34.341
and framing Lord Qing,

05:34.871 --> 05:38.341
wouldn't it be better to suffer less?

05:38.721 --> 05:39.901
Eunuch Wang,

05:40.491 --> 05:42.381
I've seen every trick in the book.

05:42.991 --> 05:44.701
If I write a confession,

05:45.431 --> 05:47.051
I'm as good as dead.

05:47.651 --> 05:49.221
What other ruthless tricks do you have?

05:49.751 --> 05:51.411
Just bring it on.

05:58.251 --> 05:59.731
His Majesty hasn't approved torture.

06:00.521 --> 06:02.190
If you were found out

06:02.191 --> 06:04.051
of using coercion,

06:04.081 --> 06:05.581
it would be improper.

06:08.961 --> 06:11.171
Don't think you can play both sides.

06:11.471 --> 06:15.701
So, what do you think I should do?

06:18.251 --> 06:19.651
I wouldn't dare to suggest anything.

06:28.311 --> 06:29.851
I know

06:30.111 --> 06:32.461
you're a stubborn fellow.

06:32.721 --> 06:35.901
But it won't help here.

06:36.921 --> 06:41.581
This thing can melt

06:41.841 --> 06:44.261
a stubborn heart.

07:16.351 --> 07:19.701
The Emperor's whims are justice.

07:20.161 --> 07:21.941
Aren't you afraid of death?

07:22.551 --> 07:26.781
What about the 237 members

07:26.991 --> 07:28.581
of your family, young and old?

07:28.751 --> 07:30.851
Aren't they afraid of death?

07:37.551 --> 07:38.971
- Yantang...
- Uncle.

07:39.401 --> 07:41.021
- Uncle.
- It was you.

07:42.301 --> 07:43.160
It wasn't me.

07:43.161 --> 07:44.411
- Help me.
- Uncle.

07:45.481 --> 07:46.621
Help.

07:49.041 --> 07:50.181
Save me.

07:52.431 --> 07:54.990
What did your parents and brother

07:54.991 --> 07:55.990
do wrong?

07:55.991 --> 07:57.531
Can your conscience rest easy

07:57.721 --> 07:59.491
knowing they'll be executed
because of you?

08:00.991 --> 08:03.021
Is one person's innocence worth

08:04.191 --> 08:08.491
the lives of your loved ones?

08:13.311 --> 08:14.190
Yantang,

08:14.191 --> 08:15.491
what are you doing?

08:16.281 --> 08:18.491
I don't need to know anything else.

08:18.551 --> 08:21.411
I only need to stir your emotions.

08:21.791 --> 08:24.211
Compared to a thousand cuts,

08:24.281 --> 08:27.381
this incense will heighten
your emotions.

08:27.751 --> 08:29.581
Combined with the poison of hatred,

08:29.961 --> 08:31.851
it will make you wish for death.

08:32.081 --> 08:36.491
Enjoy the slow agony
of the poison, Your Grace.

08:59.521 --> 09:00.661
Yantang...

09:02.881 --> 09:04.021
Yantang...

09:04.361 --> 09:05.501
Yantang.

09:50.971 --> 09:53.641
♪The glitter of the beautiful terrace
is just a fleeting splendor♪

09:54.191 --> 09:56.881
♪The army halts at your command♪

09:57.521 --> 09:59.141
♪Bending down for a single kiss♪

09:59.831 --> 10:00.971
Yantang?

10:03.591 --> 10:04.891
Ms. Longevity...

10:07.341 --> 10:10.441
♪In this life, oh♪

10:10.591 --> 10:12.291
♪Without you♪

10:12.791 --> 10:14.341
Are you here to fetch me?

10:14.361 --> 10:15.891
You're here to pick me up.

10:16.351 --> 10:18.830
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

10:18.831 --> 10:23.150
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

10:23.151 --> 10:25.340
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

10:25.341 --> 10:29.791
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

10:29.941 --> 10:33.141
♪The splendor of the world
is but fleeting sorrow♪

10:34.551 --> 10:35.470
Madam!

10:35.471 --> 10:37.160
Madam, are you all right? Madam!

10:37.161 --> 10:39.581
Madam, don't scare me!

10:39.701 --> 10:40.841
Madam!

10:42.731 --> 10:44.940
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

10:44.941 --> 10:49.531
♪Leaving the world behind♪

10:49.921 --> 10:51.061
Yantang!

10:53.471 --> 10:54.611
Yantang!

10:55.791 --> 10:59.210
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

10:59.211 --> 11:00.060
Yantang.

11:00.061 --> 11:02.731
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

11:04.951 --> 11:06.091
Yantang!

11:41.811 --> 11:48.211
♪I'll embrace the world for you
with my heart wide open♪

11:48.371 --> 11:54.901
♪No judgment will change me♪

11:55.431 --> 12:01.591
♪Only for you, I shall paint
with bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

12:01.751 --> 12:03.621
♪And for all else♪

12:03.661 --> 12:10.181
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

12:26.261 --> 12:28.221
Ms. Longevity, you're finally awake.

12:28.881 --> 12:29.720
Grandmother!

12:29.721 --> 12:30.891
Ms. Longevity is awake!

12:33.791 --> 12:34.931
Don't rush.

12:39.671 --> 12:41.181
- Ms. Longevity.
- Be careful.

12:42.951 --> 12:44.181
Grandmother.

12:44.951 --> 12:46.091
Zhangru.

12:48.671 --> 12:50.341
How did I get here?

12:50.941 --> 12:53.011
Jianming sent you here.

12:53.221 --> 12:54.880
He has made the necessary arrangements.

12:54.881 --> 12:56.661
He said this place is the safest.

12:59.791 --> 13:00.971
Yantang.

13:02.761 --> 13:03.901
Don't worry.

13:04.401 --> 13:07.421
Yantang is a blessed child.

13:08.241 --> 13:10.541
His Majesty is not a foolish ruler.

13:10.951 --> 13:12.371
He'll make a wise decision.

13:12.951 --> 13:14.731
The Cui Clan
has over a hundred officials.

13:15.071 --> 13:17.771
You have a lot of people backing you.

13:17.951 --> 13:20.170
Just focus

13:20.171 --> 13:22.041
on recovering here.

13:24.551 --> 13:25.691
How's my child?

13:26.121 --> 13:27.581
Your child is safe.

13:27.911 --> 13:29.461
The physician said

13:29.471 --> 13:31.491
you're now overwhelmed
by your emotions and energy,

13:31.641 --> 13:33.131
overly worried and anxious,

13:33.161 --> 13:35.771
and your body is very weak.

13:35.921 --> 13:37.811
You need to rest and recuperate

13:37.821 --> 13:40.011
to avoid leaving any lasting effects
from this illness.

13:42.071 --> 13:44.421
Come, lie down,

13:48.361 --> 13:49.971
and get proper rest.

13:50.311 --> 13:51.451
Grandmother.

13:51.761 --> 13:52.901
Slowly.

14:33.341 --> 14:35.830
(Xianqing Gate)

14:35.831 --> 14:36.971
Stop it!

14:37.281 --> 14:39.251
You can't just randomly strike
the Dengwen Drum!

14:39.471 --> 14:43.221
It was set up by the founding emperor

14:43.641 --> 14:45.461
to allow open speech

14:45.921 --> 14:47.481
and ensure fairness.

14:47.961 --> 14:51.981
The Ministry of Imperial Ceremony
has no right to stop me from pleading.

14:55.041 --> 14:56.821
Song Mo set fires and hurt people.

14:57.001 --> 14:58.821
So many witnessed it.

14:58.951 --> 15:01.581
How can you call it unjust,
Official Dou?

15:03.071 --> 15:04.750
You're publicly defaming the court.

15:04.751 --> 15:05.660
Take him away!

15:05.661 --> 15:08.091
- Give Song Mo a fair trial!
- Stop!

15:08.121 --> 15:09.611
Facts lie in the hearts of the people.

15:09.641 --> 15:11.581
The truth isn't for you to decide.

15:12.431 --> 15:13.360
It was I

15:13.361 --> 15:15.581
who allowed Official Dou
to strike the drum.

15:16.001 --> 15:18.400
Eunuch Wang, do you intend

15:18.401 --> 15:20.891
to take me away too?

15:24.951 --> 15:26.461
I dare not.

15:27.761 --> 15:29.461
Why are you still here?

15:29.921 --> 15:31.061
Yes, Your Highness.

15:34.641 --> 15:35.781
Let's go!

15:40.761 --> 15:41.880
Official Dou.

15:41.881 --> 15:43.311
Your Highness.

15:45.981 --> 15:47.981
Thank you, Your Highness.

15:48.771 --> 15:51.491
I acted on my own.

15:52.801 --> 15:54.541
I dare not implicate Your Highness.

15:54.551 --> 15:55.971
Song Mo is loyal and brave.

15:56.041 --> 15:57.891
Official Dou,
you're a pure-hearted minister.

15:57.921 --> 16:00.581
I should protect people like you
for the court's sake.

16:03.041 --> 16:04.421
It's a blessing to the people

16:05.521 --> 16:07.611
to have a Crown Prince like you.

16:08.591 --> 16:12.371
I hope Your Highness
will convey to His Majesty

16:13.311 --> 16:14.731
not to wrong

16:15.711 --> 16:17.301
the loyal and virtuous.

16:21.441 --> 16:23.360
(Harmony of Moral and Nourishing)
Rumors are spreading in the capital

16:23.361 --> 16:24.880
that Yunfei Silverhouse
is engaging in corrupt activities.

16:24.881 --> 16:26.831
The Dengwen Drum shouldn't
be sounded without a just cause.

16:26.841 --> 16:28.061
It has been discovered

16:28.361 --> 16:29.891
that Lu's Dental Clinic

16:30.241 --> 16:31.381
is owned

16:31.951 --> 16:33.251
by Lord Qing.

16:34.721 --> 16:36.790
It is lavishly decorated
and extremely extravagant.

16:36.791 --> 16:40.421
The silver stored there equals
half a year's taxes from Northern Zhili.

16:40.551 --> 16:42.470
Brother claims to live simply
and frugally.

16:42.471 --> 16:43.701
So,

16:43.831 --> 16:46.581
where did all this silver come from?

16:47.551 --> 16:49.120
The shop attendants also identified

16:49.121 --> 16:51.221
those entering the secret chamber.

16:51.921 --> 16:56.011
Grand Secretary Dou
and Grand Secretary Mu were both seen.

16:58.281 --> 17:00.131
Such distortion of truth and slander

17:00.401 --> 17:02.221
against the royal family
and court officials.

17:02.521 --> 17:06.101
I ask that this must
be thoroughly investigated

17:06.121 --> 17:06.990
to uphold justice.

17:06.991 --> 17:09.001
Losing the people's trust means
losing the country.

17:09.011 --> 17:10.030
Grand Secretary Dou,

17:10.031 --> 17:12.221
do you still not understand
the situation?

17:12.231 --> 17:13.801
The people are very agitated right now.

17:13.811 --> 17:16.531
I advise you not to go
against the public will.

17:18.271 --> 17:21.101
This petition is full of signatures.

17:21.471 --> 17:23.971
This is the voice of the people!

17:30.801 --> 17:32.191
The people's petition demands

17:32.411 --> 17:34.820
a thorough investigation
of Yunfei Silverhouse's alliances,

17:34.821 --> 17:36.381
corruption, and bribery cases

17:36.551 --> 17:38.021
to uncover the truth for the public.

17:38.031 --> 17:40.180
The guilty should be punished
and the innocent freed.

17:40.181 --> 17:41.700
Whether they are royals
or high-ranking officials,

17:41.701 --> 17:43.921
everyone should be treated equally
without leniency.

17:43.951 --> 17:46.761
Grand Secretaries Dou and Mu,

17:46.851 --> 17:48.161
what do you say?

17:49.561 --> 17:52.521
Dou Shiying slandered the prince

17:52.581 --> 17:54.001
and manipulated public opinion

17:54.221 --> 17:55.961
to save his son-in-law.

17:56.461 --> 17:58.441
Such interference in state affairs

17:59.701 --> 18:01.681
deserves severe punishment.

18:02.101 --> 18:03.601
If he succeeds,

18:03.781 --> 18:07.081
what becomes
of the royal family's dignity?

18:08.861 --> 18:10.401
Interfering with state affairs?

18:10.701 --> 18:13.761
Are you talking about yourself
or someone else?

18:15.101 --> 18:17.721
If only royals can handle royal matters,

18:17.941 --> 18:19.940
perhaps you should step aside

18:19.941 --> 18:23.050
and let me assist Brother
with his decrees

18:23.051 --> 18:24.711
and reviews.

18:27.781 --> 18:29.820
You've never cared about state affairs

18:29.821 --> 18:31.300
and enjoyed a carefree life.

18:31.301 --> 18:32.420
So,

18:32.421 --> 18:35.001
why have you come to the Yuxi Palace
to joke around today?

18:35.261 --> 18:38.081
I'm here out of concern for Youting.

18:39.061 --> 18:42.001
Youting has been slandered so badly

18:42.221 --> 18:45.161
that the royal family's dignity
and honor are already tarnished.

18:46.181 --> 18:47.220
Of course,

18:47.221 --> 18:49.521
we must investigate thoroughly

18:49.581 --> 18:52.481
to restore
the royal family's reputation.

18:56.941 --> 18:59.100
The Grand Princess makes a valid point.

18:59.101 --> 19:00.740
The Censorate suggests delaying

19:00.741 --> 19:03.740
the conviction of Song Mo

19:03.741 --> 19:06.060
since the faction list circulating

19:06.061 --> 19:07.420
among the people is unreliable.

19:07.421 --> 19:10.390
But the bribery accounts presented
by Song Mo

19:10.391 --> 19:12.551
are verifiable.

19:12.661 --> 19:13.940
To calm the public,

19:13.941 --> 19:17.140
I propose using these accounts
as a starting point

19:17.141 --> 19:18.721
to audit the Six Ministries,

19:18.781 --> 19:21.820
focusing on the Diannan Bureau
under the Ministry of Revenue

19:21.821 --> 19:23.901
and the Auditing Office
under the Ministry of Works.

19:34.261 --> 19:37.460
Liang Jifang, the Ministry of Justice,
and the Censorate

19:37.461 --> 19:39.041
have been working tirelessly for days.

19:39.381 --> 19:41.201
If they keep investigating,

19:41.821 --> 19:45.601
Youting's involvement
in bribery will be concrete

19:46.041 --> 19:48.961
and Song Mo's arson will seem justified.

19:49.421 --> 19:51.140
The couple in Yizhi Hall

19:51.141 --> 19:53.441
has truly played their cards well.

19:53.861 --> 19:55.001
Your Majesty,

19:55.661 --> 19:57.340
given the current situation,

19:57.341 --> 19:59.641
there's no way to back out unscathed.

20:00.181 --> 20:01.441
For the greater good,

20:01.621 --> 20:04.241
His Highness must be kept out of this.

20:05.901 --> 20:07.521
You mean

20:08.221 --> 20:10.820
we should offer Liang Jifang
a new scapegoat?

20:10.821 --> 20:12.940
Dou Shishu has been the one managing

20:12.941 --> 20:15.081
Silverhouse's bribery, alliances,
and secret deals.

20:15.581 --> 20:16.761
He even managed

20:17.061 --> 20:18.521
the horse market trade.

20:20.061 --> 20:23.140
I remember you had a fallout

20:23.141 --> 20:26.201
with Dou Shishu over your son.

20:27.341 --> 20:28.300
This is a grave matter.

20:28.301 --> 20:30.420
I wouldn't dare use it
for personal revenge.

20:30.421 --> 20:32.540
What I say is true.

20:32.541 --> 20:33.940
No one but Grand Secretary Dou

20:33.941 --> 20:35.300
can bear the weight of this matter.

20:35.301 --> 20:36.380
Everything that I do

20:36.381 --> 20:38.721
is for His Highness
and Your Majesty's sake.

20:41.861 --> 20:45.241
Dou Shishu was recommended by Shude.

20:45.861 --> 20:47.201
Let her accompany him

20:48.461 --> 20:49.841
to the end,

20:50.261 --> 20:51.721
so he won't be lonely.

21:00.251 --> 21:01.231
It's been a long time

21:01.241 --> 21:03.110
since I've seen you dress up
so meticulously.

21:03.111 --> 21:05.771
Who are you meeting today, Master?

21:10.341 --> 21:12.111
In one's lifetime,

21:12.421 --> 21:13.701
one should arrive with dignity

21:14.211 --> 21:15.621
and depart with dignity.

21:17.661 --> 21:19.211
You don't have to come with me.

21:23.621 --> 21:26.481
(Soaring to Great Heights)

21:34.581 --> 21:36.761
May heaven bless
the Dou Clan of the North Tower

21:37.341 --> 21:38.961
with high-ranking officials

21:39.141 --> 21:40.641
and prosperity for generations,

21:41.581 --> 21:44.441
illuminating all corners of the land,

21:44.781 --> 21:48.521
where the old year ends
and the new one begins.

21:48.821 --> 21:50.781
You've built yourself a Wenyuan Pavilion

21:50.821 --> 21:52.580
just to secure the position
of Chief Grand Secretary.

21:52.581 --> 21:54.361
You're completely obsessed.

21:59.901 --> 22:01.161
I thought you said you quit.

22:04.341 --> 22:06.561
Whenever I face difficulties,

22:07.821 --> 22:09.881
I like to sit here and remind myself

22:10.581 --> 22:12.441
to exercise restraint

22:13.381 --> 22:14.601
and patience.

22:15.021 --> 22:17.481
Only by truly sitting in this chair

22:18.181 --> 22:19.681
can I relax.

22:21.181 --> 22:22.321
Now,

22:23.331 --> 22:25.081
I'm just one step away.

22:25.421 --> 22:28.201
You must already knew
you can't cross that step.

22:33.901 --> 22:36.241
Mu Chuan deliberately exposed flaws,

22:36.711 --> 22:39.920
claiming I used Lord Qing's name
for corruption.

22:39.921 --> 22:42.071
The Empress is sacrificing me

22:43.211 --> 22:45.221
to save herself.

22:46.291 --> 22:48.391
You've always been cautious.

22:48.731 --> 22:50.721
Did you never consider

22:51.011 --> 22:53.250
you might be used as a scapegoat
after all these years?

22:53.251 --> 22:54.681
I find that hard to believe.

22:57.071 --> 23:00.881
When the three Zhuge brothers joined
Wei, Han, and Wu, respectively,

23:02.621 --> 23:04.321
how could I push Shiying

23:05.501 --> 23:07.361
in the opposite direction

23:07.581 --> 23:09.241
without being a scapegoat?

23:09.861 --> 23:11.401
I submitted the evidence against me

23:11.701 --> 23:13.681
to the Grand Secretariat

23:13.741 --> 23:15.241
under Shiying's name.

23:16.021 --> 23:17.981
He will be praised for his loyalty
to the throne

23:18.941 --> 23:20.250
and rewarded for exposing me.

23:20.251 --> 23:24.001
The Crown Prince
will admire and trust him.

23:25.581 --> 23:28.001
In the next reign,
his name will surely

23:28.541 --> 23:30.381
be among the ministers.

23:30.541 --> 23:32.521
The Dou Family's future generation

23:32.701 --> 23:35.141
will secure their place in that chair.

23:43.461 --> 23:45.041
By the Empress's decree!

23:45.621 --> 23:49.041
Arrest the traitor
Dou Shishu immediately!

23:54.541 --> 23:56.201
I helped you back then

23:56.261 --> 23:58.761
because your talent shouldn't be buried.

23:59.141 --> 24:01.001
If you renounce your ways now,

24:01.061 --> 24:03.281
I'll plead for your life
before the Emperor

24:04.181 --> 24:05.820
and have you exiled to a quiet place,

24:05.821 --> 24:08.161
so you can write your books in peace.

24:11.861 --> 24:13.201
This time,

24:14.301 --> 24:16.361
Your Highness can't help me.

24:17.261 --> 24:18.401
But

24:19.021 --> 24:20.561
I can do

24:21.141 --> 24:22.281
one last thing

24:23.181 --> 24:24.801
for Your Highness.

24:34.181 --> 24:35.361
Put down your weapons

24:35.541 --> 24:37.041
and tell Dou Shiying to come here.

24:44.621 --> 24:46.420
Brother, drop the dagger.

24:46.421 --> 24:47.561
They're framing you.

24:47.581 --> 24:49.380
I'll go with you to the Censorate
and clear your name.

24:49.381 --> 24:50.881
Don't pretend to care!

24:51.621 --> 24:52.761
Dou Shiying,

24:53.421 --> 24:54.980
I was blind to trust you.

24:54.981 --> 24:58.140
I didn't expect that you had been collecting
evidence against me,

24:58.141 --> 24:59.540
waiting to betray me

24:59.541 --> 25:01.521
for wealth and power.

25:01.621 --> 25:05.841
I supported and looked after you.

25:06.181 --> 25:07.780
But you turned out

25:07.781 --> 25:08.980
to be a venomous snake!

25:08.981 --> 25:10.140
Brother, you...

25:10.141 --> 25:11.231
Shut up!

25:11.241 --> 25:13.011
The day you drew
the sword on me in public,

25:13.101 --> 25:15.481
our brotherhood was severed!

25:16.661 --> 25:19.161
Dou Shishu is holding a royal hostage.

25:19.221 --> 25:20.721
Kill him on the spot!

25:20.941 --> 25:22.081
Release the arrows!

25:22.581 --> 25:24.001
No, don't!

25:32.181 --> 25:34.081
Brother!

25:40.981 --> 25:42.121
Yizhen,

25:43.021 --> 25:45.001
stop opposing the Empress.

25:46.341 --> 25:48.441
Return to your fief.

25:49.181 --> 25:51.121
When the crape myrtle trees bear fruit,

25:51.581 --> 25:54.921
eat some for me.

25:59.061 --> 26:00.201
Yuanji.

26:01.261 --> 26:03.361
Yuanji!

26:13.341 --> 26:14.681
Yuanji...

26:15.821 --> 26:17.641
Yuanji...

26:21.701 --> 26:22.860
(Notice)

26:22.861 --> 26:25.220
The traitor Dou Shishu abused his power

26:25.221 --> 26:26.801
and embezzled the people's wealth.

26:26.901 --> 26:28.241
His crimes were unforgivable,

26:28.341 --> 26:29.860
and he has been executed.

26:29.861 --> 26:31.951
The stolen funds
have been returned to the treasury

26:31.961 --> 26:33.201
as a warning to others!

26:33.421 --> 26:35.841
- Good!
- Well done!

26:37.421 --> 26:38.300
He's better off dead!

26:38.301 --> 26:39.641
- Nice work!
- That's right!

27:11.861 --> 27:14.481
He caused chaos all his life,

27:15.261 --> 27:16.801
and in the end,

27:17.541 --> 27:20.121
he's just decorating this room.

27:22.741 --> 27:23.620
(Weigh gains against losses,)

27:23.621 --> 27:26.100
(success against failure.)
That quote from Zhuge Liang

27:26.101 --> 27:27.241
(Dou Shishu)

27:27.261 --> 27:30.881
was prepared for you
to take a different path.

27:32.021 --> 27:33.201
Shishu wanted

27:34.101 --> 27:36.561
to push me toward the Crown Prince

27:37.581 --> 27:40.641
to ensure the future glory
of the Dou Family.

27:41.781 --> 27:43.881
If I had taken on this burden earlier

27:44.581 --> 27:46.201
to fight for the Dou Family,

27:47.061 --> 27:50.561
Shishu wouldn't have made

27:50.981 --> 27:52.201
so many mistakes.

27:55.021 --> 27:56.161
Shiying,

27:57.181 --> 27:59.081
we need to look forward.

28:00.261 --> 28:02.401
Whether you take up the post in Chanxi

28:03.181 --> 28:06.481
or resign from the court,

28:07.061 --> 28:08.641
just make a decision.

28:11.421 --> 28:12.881
Shishu is gone.

28:14.141 --> 28:15.761
Lord Qing and the Empress

28:16.941 --> 28:19.041
won't let the Dou family off easily.

28:23.781 --> 28:25.121
I cannot hide.

28:26.141 --> 28:29.601
I must protect everyone
in this household.

28:30.221 --> 28:32.041
The Crown Prince promised to protect us.

28:32.501 --> 28:33.801
All the more reason

28:34.341 --> 28:35.961
we can't let the Crown Prince

28:36.781 --> 28:39.681
be accused of favoritism
in this turbulent time.

28:40.261 --> 28:41.401
Good.

28:43.221 --> 28:45.361
Use my disaster relief commendation

28:45.581 --> 28:48.180
and join with the students
and officials of the Cui Clan of Ji'an

28:48.181 --> 28:49.961
to submit a petition.

28:49.981 --> 28:51.121
That's right.

28:51.301 --> 28:54.401
Also, Ms. Longevity's
potato cultivation to combat famine

28:54.581 --> 28:56.780
and Song Mo's achievements
in quelling the pirates

28:56.781 --> 28:58.161
will all be brought up,

28:58.581 --> 29:00.521
and let all the officials see

29:00.661 --> 29:04.081
how much the Dou Family has done
for the court.

29:04.251 --> 29:05.611
I will draft the petition now.

29:16.581 --> 29:18.481
By the Empress's decree!

29:18.661 --> 29:20.921
Song Mo is guilty of negligence,

29:20.981 --> 29:23.201
resulting in the incident
on Changle Street.

29:23.741 --> 29:26.561
However, considering his merits
in quelling the pirates,

29:26.781 --> 29:28.820
he shall be released from prison

29:28.821 --> 29:31.180
and immediately confined to Yizhi Hall,

29:31.181 --> 29:33.681
awaiting further decisions!

29:35.941 --> 29:37.521
Fifth Uncle is dead.

29:38.181 --> 29:39.761
Grand Princess Shude returned

29:39.981 --> 29:42.001
to her fief without a word.

29:43.101 --> 29:44.681
Once His Majesty wakes up,

29:45.261 --> 29:47.321
the court will surely change.

29:48.021 --> 29:50.220
Fifth Uncle was supposed
to have the right connections,

29:50.221 --> 29:51.761
a position of great power.

29:52.341 --> 29:55.081
Though we couldn't expose
those behind him,

29:56.421 --> 29:58.961
at least we've fought against fate.

30:02.381 --> 30:04.841
As for when His Majesty will wake

30:05.301 --> 30:07.921
and if he can help you,

30:08.781 --> 30:09.921
I dare not make a guess.

30:10.821 --> 30:12.601
I had hoped

30:13.341 --> 30:14.601
we could see

30:15.301 --> 30:17.681
the magnolias bloom together
at least once more.

30:19.621 --> 30:21.241
But with all this snow,

30:21.821 --> 30:23.001
I wonder

30:23.621 --> 30:26.441
if the branches will survive.

30:27.621 --> 30:29.041
If you feel like it,

30:29.691 --> 30:32.161
I'll ask them to bring two cloaks,

30:32.501 --> 30:33.881
and we can go see.

30:34.461 --> 30:35.801
It's no use.

30:38.061 --> 30:40.521
I've been stripped of my title

30:41.021 --> 30:42.361
and confined to my residence.

30:42.861 --> 30:46.001
Lu Ming and General Yan
are also imprisoned.

30:46.461 --> 30:49.961
The place is surrounded
by Shadow Guards.

30:50.481 --> 30:52.441
It's good that the Shadow Guard
is keeping watch.

30:53.011 --> 30:56.001
The guards may restrict us.
But they also protect us.

30:56.211 --> 30:58.561
At least, Yizhi Hall is safe.

31:00.941 --> 31:02.761
After all these years of planning,

31:03.181 --> 31:05.001
we've reached this point.

31:05.781 --> 31:08.801
We've done everything we could.

31:10.541 --> 31:12.081
Now, we can just wait

31:12.831 --> 31:14.521
for the flowers to bloom

31:16.501 --> 31:18.601
and enjoy some peace.

31:21.911 --> 31:23.051
Give me your hand.

31:37.481 --> 31:40.291
The court is in the midst of selecting
the head of the Imperial Guard.

31:40.301 --> 31:42.161
It's a time of great unrest,

31:42.701 --> 31:43.961
and if we are to move troops,

31:44.581 --> 31:46.881
now is the best opportunity.

31:47.681 --> 31:50.351
The forces in Liaodong
aren't fully prepared yet.

31:50.411 --> 31:53.641
Wouldn't it be too soon to act now?

31:55.281 --> 31:56.540
During the Xuanwu Gate incident,

31:56.541 --> 31:58.511
Emperor Taizong used
only eight hundred soldiers.

31:58.541 --> 31:59.971
It's not about the size of the army,

32:00.061 --> 32:01.201
but

32:02.221 --> 32:03.601
about the right timing.

32:09.461 --> 32:11.231
What do you think, Commander Song?

32:11.911 --> 32:13.601
As long as Song Mo lives,

32:14.101 --> 32:15.721
he remains a threat.

32:17.301 --> 32:19.561
This is also my concern.

32:19.741 --> 32:21.500
Song Mo is heavily poisoned,

32:21.501 --> 32:23.401
and his strength is greatly weakened.

32:23.661 --> 32:26.321
His allies are imprisoned.

32:26.581 --> 32:28.361
He can't stir up much trouble.

32:28.621 --> 32:30.961
Song Mo and Dou Zhao seem calm now.

32:31.301 --> 32:33.001
But it's all an act.

32:33.021 --> 32:34.961
They surely have
something else up their sleeves.

32:35.141 --> 32:36.991
I've sent people
to keep a close watch on them,

32:37.001 --> 32:38.551
waiting for the right moment to strike.

32:38.981 --> 32:41.201
Then I shall wait for your good news.

32:41.751 --> 32:43.061
All we need now

32:43.631 --> 32:45.681
is a good chance.

32:54.001 --> 32:55.401
You seem to have

32:55.561 --> 32:58.031
some hostility toward Song Han.

32:58.181 --> 32:59.881
Is it because of Dou Zhao?

33:00.221 --> 33:02.121
Dou Zhao and I share a close friendship.

33:02.251 --> 33:04.801
Your Highness should understand this.

33:05.381 --> 33:06.721
As for Song Han,

33:08.381 --> 33:11.081
he's blinded by personal vendettas
and lacks foresight.

33:11.121 --> 33:12.481
He doesn't think about the future.

33:12.861 --> 33:14.481
Whatever he says to Your Highness

33:14.701 --> 33:16.161
is of no concern to me.

33:16.381 --> 33:17.601
Such grace from you, Teacher.

33:20.701 --> 33:22.081
But aren't you worried?

33:23.381 --> 33:25.121
The Duke of Ying is confined,

33:25.251 --> 33:26.641
but he hasn't been convicted.

33:27.061 --> 33:30.041
Chief Grand Secretary Liang Jifang
is also the Crown Prince's tutor.

33:30.181 --> 33:31.881
They praise good deeds publicly

33:32.101 --> 33:33.601
and correct mistakes privately.

33:34.301 --> 33:36.780
Either Song Han mistreats
his brother and sister-in-law,

33:36.781 --> 33:38.380
causing Song Mo to die from poison,

33:38.381 --> 33:41.681
or Song Mo kills his brother in a rage
to protect his wife.

33:42.661 --> 33:44.201
No matter how much blood is spilled,

33:44.301 --> 33:46.881
it's a family affair
of the Duke of Ying's household

33:47.781 --> 33:49.841
and has nothing to do
with Your Highness.

33:50.541 --> 33:52.561
The Shadow Guards are keeping
a strict watch.

33:52.821 --> 33:54.841
So they can't escape this cage.

33:55.581 --> 33:57.721
Rather than worrying
about Song Mo and his wife,

33:58.061 --> 34:00.961
Your Highness should think
about His Majesty's health.

34:01.261 --> 34:02.681
If His Majesty wakes up

34:03.021 --> 34:04.481
and issues a decree,

34:04.741 --> 34:08.041
that would truly be detrimental
to Your Highness.

34:15.571 --> 34:17.161
There's enough for everyone.

34:17.631 --> 34:18.841
So please be patient.

34:18.851 --> 34:20.340
Be patient. Everyone will have theirs.

34:20.341 --> 34:21.380
- Thank you, Your Highness.
- Here you go.

34:21.381 --> 34:22.300
Princess,

34:22.301 --> 34:24.321
why do you have
to serve the congee yourself?

34:24.341 --> 34:25.980
You can leave

34:25.981 --> 34:27.460
this task to the servant.

34:27.461 --> 34:28.880
- Be careful.
- Thank you.

34:28.881 --> 34:31.180
I used to do this often
when I was a merchant.

34:31.181 --> 34:32.500
Now that I'm a princess,

34:32.501 --> 34:33.580
I should do more.

34:33.581 --> 34:36.161
That's the only way to live up
to the title His Majesty gave me.

34:36.781 --> 34:39.001
- Here.
- You're so kind to the people.

34:39.541 --> 34:41.281
It's truly a blessing for all.

34:44.341 --> 34:46.881
(Besides, doing this helps atone)

34:47.381 --> 34:49.481
(for Muyu's bloodshed.)

34:50.181 --> 34:51.481
(Only by doing so,)

34:51.821 --> 34:53.201
(can I find some peace.)

34:53.941 --> 34:55.010
Next.

34:55.011 --> 34:55.870
Here you go.

34:55.871 --> 34:57.041
- Thank you.
- Don't drop it.

34:58.711 --> 35:00.121
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

35:00.281 --> 35:02.001
Thank you. Thank...

35:06.091 --> 35:07.231
Wait!

35:11.341 --> 35:13.521
Princess, what's the matter?

35:14.141 --> 35:15.801
You don't look too well.

35:16.341 --> 35:18.121
Are you not feeling well?

35:20.341 --> 35:21.481
I'm fine.

35:23.861 --> 35:26.041
He's just a mere
unarmed carriage driver.

35:26.301 --> 35:28.001
After dispatching so many people

35:28.211 --> 35:29.561
and such a long time,

35:30.401 --> 35:31.961
you still haven't found him.

35:33.741 --> 35:35.601
What's the use of having guards
like you?

35:36.141 --> 35:39.281
That carriage driver
is as slippery as an eel.

35:39.461 --> 35:42.361
He might've fled
outside the capital by now.

35:43.581 --> 35:45.721
Should we expand the search

35:47.221 --> 35:48.601
beyond the capital?

35:51.021 --> 35:52.891
(Striving with Grace)
Are you teaching me what to do?

35:53.901 --> 35:56.481
I dare not. Forgive me.

36:01.101 --> 36:02.241
Princess.

36:07.341 --> 36:09.121
Why did you come
without announcing yourself?

36:11.501 --> 36:13.521
Your hand is so cold,

36:13.661 --> 36:14.801
and you look pale too.

36:15.421 --> 36:16.561
Come here.

36:21.061 --> 36:22.361
I shall take my leave.

36:25.261 --> 36:27.921
Did anything happen today?

36:28.581 --> 36:30.780
Princess almost fainted
when she was serving congee

36:30.781 --> 36:32.321
- at the alms booth.
- Directress Su,

36:35.501 --> 36:37.041
please leave us.

36:37.341 --> 36:38.481
Yes.

36:41.141 --> 36:43.401
Directress Su exaggerated.

36:44.641 --> 36:46.921
Maybe I almost fainted

36:47.821 --> 36:49.761
because I stood too long
and got too tired.

36:54.981 --> 36:56.121
My mother

36:57.461 --> 36:58.641
was like that too.

36:59.341 --> 37:02.841
Many illnesses
don't show symptoms at first.

37:04.621 --> 37:05.580
This won't do.

37:05.581 --> 37:07.001
I'm fetching the imperial physician.

37:07.061 --> 37:08.201
It's all right.

37:08.381 --> 37:09.681
I'm fine.

37:11.701 --> 37:13.761
I know my own body well.

37:20.021 --> 37:21.161
All right.

37:21.741 --> 37:22.881
Anything you say.

37:25.381 --> 37:27.081
(Yizhi Hall)
Thank you for working hard, officers.

37:27.101 --> 37:29.180
This is wine brewed
in the Duke of Ying's Residence,

37:29.181 --> 37:30.901
as a token of appreciation
for both of you.

37:34.821 --> 37:35.820
It's such a fine wine!

37:35.821 --> 37:37.801
Thank the Commander on our behalf.

37:37.821 --> 37:38.961
Many thanks.

37:40.021 --> 37:41.961
(To be read by Commander Song)
We couldn't eliminate them before.

37:41.981 --> 37:43.641
With the Shadow Guards protecting them,

37:43.981 --> 37:46.361
it's almost impossible.

37:53.131 --> 37:54.921
I noticed you haven't eaten all day.

37:55.221 --> 37:56.681
So I made you some dessert.

38:11.501 --> 38:13.100
Didn't the Empress ask you

38:13.101 --> 38:15.220
to keep Song Mo alive?

38:15.221 --> 38:18.041
The Empress is probably worried
about Song Mo's old followers.

38:18.521 --> 38:19.721
Such unnecessary compassion.

38:19.731 --> 38:21.521
The Tengxiang Guard
is under my control now.

38:21.541 --> 38:23.201
Why fear a bunch of defeated soldiers?

38:23.671 --> 38:26.721
As long as we build solid connections
with the noble families in the capital,

38:26.941 --> 38:28.081
even Lord Qing

38:28.301 --> 38:29.971
won't dare challenge me easily.

38:31.501 --> 38:32.641
Of course.

38:33.061 --> 38:35.641
Socializing with nobles is costly.

38:35.941 --> 38:37.540
Zhao holds a 70% stake

38:37.541 --> 38:38.921
in Miao family's shop.

38:39.411 --> 38:41.121
If she's willing to loosen her grip,

38:41.261 --> 38:42.881
we'd be much better off financially.

38:44.341 --> 38:45.481
Ansu,

38:45.901 --> 38:47.121
I know what you're planning.

38:48.741 --> 38:50.121
You want to use that money

38:51.141 --> 38:52.481
to stop me from harming Dou Zhao.

38:53.101 --> 38:54.241
Am I right?

39:02.341 --> 39:03.921
Dou Zhao is cunning and full of schemes.

39:04.501 --> 39:05.761
If I don't do anything,

39:06.181 --> 39:07.380
she will harm us.

39:07.381 --> 39:09.201
Zhao isn't like that.

39:09.741 --> 39:11.820
Back in Futing, she helped me a lot.

39:11.821 --> 39:13.660
When the Miao Family had nothing,

39:13.661 --> 39:15.801
she stood by my side.

39:17.621 --> 39:19.641
Honestly, I'm starting
to feel a bit jealous of her

39:19.761 --> 39:21.521
for making you worry
about her this much.

39:24.301 --> 39:25.441
Muyu,

39:25.701 --> 39:28.121
promise me not to harm Zhao.

39:28.241 --> 39:30.081
I'll talk to her
about the profit adjustment.

39:30.161 --> 39:31.720
I'll make her understand the situation

39:31.721 --> 39:33.121
and stop defying you.

39:41.901 --> 39:42.740
(Yizhi Hall)

39:42.741 --> 39:45.321
I need to go inside
to discuss some family matters.

39:52.061 --> 39:54.340
(Contract. Miao Ansu)
Dou Zhao has goods with the Miao.

39:54.341 --> 39:55.900
I need to sign this contract

39:55.901 --> 39:57.060
with Dou Zhao today

39:57.061 --> 39:58.561
and discuss the profit adjustment.

39:58.741 --> 40:00.060
If you don't let me pass,

40:00.061 --> 40:01.641
the business will suffer,

40:02.061 --> 40:03.521
and I won't be able to explain it.

40:04.531 --> 40:05.560
But...

40:05.561 --> 40:06.540
Well...

40:06.541 --> 40:09.220
I had this arranged with the Commander
of the Tengxiang Guard

40:09.221 --> 40:10.971
to make Dou Zhao agree
to the profit adjustment.

40:10.981 --> 40:12.020
If you don't believe me,

40:12.021 --> 40:13.681
you can ask the Commander himself.

40:13.861 --> 40:15.761
But if someone is to be blamed for this,

40:16.501 --> 40:17.940
don't say I didn't warn you.

40:17.941 --> 40:21.041
(Yizhi Hall)

40:22.741 --> 40:23.881
Let her through!

40:23.981 --> 40:25.121
Your Highness, come this way.

40:25.541 --> 40:26.681
Please come in.

40:30.821 --> 40:33.641
I didn't expect Song Han
to trust you so much now.

40:34.081 --> 40:36.641
A courtyard
where he won't even let a fly get in,

40:37.021 --> 40:38.391
he lets you in.

40:40.021 --> 40:41.161
Zhao,

40:41.821 --> 40:45.401
when the Miao family's ship
was seized back in Futing,

40:45.661 --> 40:47.601
you paid to calm the angry crowd

40:47.821 --> 40:49.241
and even covered the initial costs.

40:50.061 --> 40:52.361
That's how we have
the Miao family's shop now.

40:52.541 --> 40:54.641
You've always had a clear perspective.

40:55.261 --> 40:56.641
But recently,

40:56.891 --> 40:57.980
I've faced some situations

40:57.981 --> 40:59.300
that I can't figure out.

40:59.301 --> 41:00.561
My mind is a mess.

41:00.621 --> 41:01.820
I need your guidance

41:01.821 --> 41:03.441
on what to do.

41:03.821 --> 41:04.961
Ansu,

41:05.821 --> 41:08.321
I know you genuinely love Song Han.

41:08.621 --> 41:10.241
But you need to see him for who he is.

41:10.661 --> 41:11.980
What Song Han is doing

41:11.981 --> 41:13.561
is treason.

41:13.781 --> 41:15.761
This won't end well.

41:18.581 --> 41:20.521
I know what you're trying to say.

41:20.941 --> 41:23.001
But as a princess now,

41:23.141 --> 41:25.081
every word and action of mine
is under scrutiny.

41:25.661 --> 41:27.081
I have no freedom.

41:31.981 --> 41:35.761
If you need help, seek out Chen Jia.

41:35.821 --> 41:37.201
He knows what to do.

41:37.221 --> 41:38.361
Chen Jia?

41:46.621 --> 41:48.761
Weren't they just discussing
profit adjustments?

41:49.591 --> 41:50.841
Why hasn't the Princess returned

41:51.391 --> 41:52.801
at this hour?

41:57.741 --> 41:59.081
Don't be afraid.

41:59.141 --> 42:01.961
I didn't bring you here to harm you.

42:02.621 --> 42:03.961
I only want to know

42:04.141 --> 42:06.001
why did you run away
the moment you saw me?

42:11.821 --> 42:13.321
Still not talking, huh?

42:13.741 --> 42:16.041
Don't blame me for being ruthless.

42:16.341 --> 42:17.921
All right, I'll talk.

42:18.621 --> 42:19.801
Master sent

42:20.101 --> 42:21.921
someone to come after my life

42:21.941 --> 42:23.020
because...

42:23.021 --> 42:24.761
Because of Young Master Anping.

42:43.721 --> 42:45.980
Once the poison takes effect,
he won't recognize anyone.

42:45.981 --> 42:48.220
Master has locked himself
in the bathhouse

42:48.221 --> 42:49.751
and won't answer the door to anyone.

42:54.341 --> 42:55.481
Yantang,

42:55.861 --> 42:59.161
it's me. I'm Ms. Longevity.

42:59.471 --> 43:03.950
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:03.951 --> 43:07.711
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:07.871 --> 43:12.261
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:12.441 --> 43:16.370
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:16.371 --> 43:19.350
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:19.351 --> 43:21.560
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

43:21.561 --> 43:24.121
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

43:24.171 --> 43:27.741
♪Your presence
my side is irreplaceable♪

43:27.801 --> 43:31.321
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

43:31.331 --> 43:35.310
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

43:35.311 --> 43:39.341
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

43:39.781 --> 43:43.241
♪Having you is a blessing♪

43:43.401 --> 43:45.581
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

43:45.601 --> 43:49.431
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

43:49.761 --> 43:52.901
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

43:53.441 --> 43:56.851
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

43:57.291 --> 44:00.831
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:01.031 --> 44:04.700
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:04.701 --> 44:09.041
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:09.101 --> 44:12.830
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:12.831 --> 44:16.310
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:16.311 --> 44:20.991
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:21.021 --> 44:24.610
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

44:24.611 --> 44:28.751
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

44:28.821 --> 44:32.111
♪Always together, looking back♪

44:32.421 --> 44:39.721
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

44:48.941 --> 44:49.900
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:49.901 --> 44:50.940
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:50.941 --> 44:52.161
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
